---

<Layout>
  <section id="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-shot">
      <Picture src={heroImg} alt={"Unitree A2"} />
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h1 class="h1">Unitree A2</h1>
      <p class="subtitle-3">Transformative Newborn</p>
    </div>
    <div class="sub-content">
      <p class="h1">
        The High-Endurance <br class="br-tablet br-mobile" /> Industrial Quadruped
        <br class="br-desktop br-mobile" />
        with <br class="br-tablet" /> Hot-Swappable <br class="br-mobile" /> Power
      </p>
      <span class="paragraph-1">
        The Unitree A2 is a reliable, agile, and lightweight industrial-grade
        robot designed for extended missions in complex and rugged environments.
      </span>

      <!-- <ButtonPrimary content="Watch Video" /> -->
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="new-section">
    <div class="content">
      <!-- <div class="line-element">
        <div></div>
        <span> Wheeled Legged Robot Dog</span>
        <div></div>
      </div> -->
      <h2 class="h1">Go Beyond The <br class="br-mobile" /> Limits</h2>
      <!-- <p>Transformative Newborn</p> -->
    </div>
    <div class="shot">
      <Picture
        src={newPic}
        alt={"A2 New Model "}
        fetchpriority={"high"}
        quality={"max"}
      />
      <div class="detail">
        <p>3 hours with <br /> 25kg load</p>
        <span>Endurance </span>
        <img src="/images/indicator.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="detail">
        <p>Max Joint Torque <br /> 180 N.m</p>
        <span>Power </span>
        <img src="/images/indicator.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="detail">
        <p>Max Step Height 30cm, <br /> 45° Slope Capability</p>
        <span> Mobility</span>
        <img src="/images/indicator.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="detail">
        <p>Dual Battery System, <br /> IP67 Core Components</p>
        <span> Reliability</span>
        <img src="/images/indicator.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <Image class={"blue-shade"} src={blue_shade} alt={""} format="webp" />
  </section>
  <section class="simple-section full-desktop full-tablet">
    <h2 class="h1">
      Agile, Swift, and <br class="br-mobile br-tablet" /> Extended <br
        class="br-desktop"
      /> Endurance
    </h2>
    <p class="paragraph-1">
      Weighing around 37kg with the battery, the A2 is designed for lightweight
      agility and marathon missions. It can continuously walk for over 5 hours
      (unloaded) or over 3 hours with a 25kg continuous walking load. This
      combination of lightweight design and high endurance makes it ideal for
      long-distance logistics and extensive inspection routes.
    </p>
    <div class="media-wrapper">
      <video playsinline muted loop preload="metadata" class="media">
        <source src="/videos/a2/0.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section
    class="simple-section shadow-type-desktop full-tablet shadow-type-mobile-regular"
  >
    <h2 class="h1">
      Dual-Sided Perception <br class="br-mobile br-tablet" /> for <br
        class="br-desktop"
      /> Zero Blind Spots
    </h2>
    <p class="paragraph-1">
      The A2 PRO model features Dual-Sided Perception, utilizing two industrial
      LiDARs (front & rear) along with an HD camera and front light. This
      configuration ensures zero blind spots and greater accuracy in
      environmental detection, enabling the robot to navigate safely and
      effectively even in highly complex or cluttered industrial settings.
    </p>
    <div class="media-wrapper">
      <Picture src={a2_1} alt={"Dual-Sided Perception for Zero Blind Spots"} />
    </div>
  </section>
  <section
    id="swap-section"
    class="simple-section overflow-hidden full-img-desktop full-img-tablet head-shot-mobile head-shot-tablet align-start-desktop"
  >
    <h2 class="h1">Hot-Swappable Dual <br /> Battery System</h2>
    <p class="paragraph-1">
      The A2 guarantees unlimited runtime through its Hot-Swappable Dual Battery
      System. The dual-battery parallel design allows for seamless battery swaps
      without powering down the robot, ensuring uninterrupted mission
      continuity—a critical feature for extreme and time-sensitive operations.
      The reliable triple power system is built to operate in temperatures
      ranging from -20℃ to 55℃.
    </p>
    <div class="media-wrapper">
      <video
        playsinline
        muted
        loop
        preload="metadata"
        class="media shot object-pos-top-desktop"
      >
        <source src="/videos/a2/1.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section
    class="simple-section full-img-desktop full-tablet margin-0 align-end-desktop p-5"
  >
    <h2 class="h1">
      Versatile Platform <br class="br-mobile" /> for <br class="br-tablet" /> Industrial
      <br class="br-desktop br-mobile" /> Development
    </h2>
    <p class="paragraph-1">
      The A2 guarantees unlimited runtime through its Hot-Swappable Dual Battery
      System. The dual-battery parallel design allows for seamless battery swaps
      without powering down the robot, ensuring uninterrupted mission
      continuity—a critical feature for extreme and time-sensitive operations.
      The reliable triple power system is built to operate in temperatures
      ranging from -20℃ to 55℃.
    </p>
