        <span> Wheel-Leg Option </span>
        <p>
          Convert the A2 to a wheeled-legged robot for increased speed and
          efficiency on flat surfaces.
        </p>
        <div class="buttons">
          <ButtonPrimary content="Add to cart" />
          <ButtonSecondary content="Learn more" />
        </div>
        <!-- <Picture
